name: Les Quartiers | Sainte-Foy (3/3)
description:
This artwork is a representation of the Sainte-Foy Neighborhood in Québec City, featuring the landmark Pyramid. I made this piece while exploring Perlin Noise and Gaussian values. It is part 3 of a series of 3 called "Les Quartiers".

Dimensions: 3200 x 3200
